702361f-a.title: Brooklyn: 4th Street (North) - Roebling Avenue
702361f-a.text:
Noirth 4th Street, north side, at Roebling Avenue. The poultry
market is at the northesst corner; the school Puhlic School No.
17--at the northwest corner.
P. L. Sperr  September 16, 1941
